{
  "stem": "2718.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the so-called [INAUDIBLE] commando-- which was part of the German industrial commando-- has-- has taken over the factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, in actual fact, no-- no Hungarian policeman-- or no Hungarians-- Hungarians had no authority over a factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Therefore--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they-- what happens is, that they put this [? stamp ?] out-- they put this-- [? stamp-- ?] they put the-- they-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they put the official papers out on the walls, and on the-- on the gates, that this was-- this was the-- under the-- under the authority of the [INAUDIBLE] commando.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that meant that there was no-- nobody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the highest authority.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were higher than the Hungarian authorities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they-- whatever we manufactured at that time went the normal way-- and went to its normal place-- but what-- what was important to them had priority.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, at that time, and what it meant for us, as a family, that the men-- my two uncles, my grandfather, and my father-- were protected in such a way that they had safe transport, they had safe-- the whole family got plenty of-- of ration tickets.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, they-- they really tried to make life a bit easier for us-- or for them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two or three officers came, and they apologized for the inconvenience, and whatever, which didn't do much good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, you know, at least it was some sort of a hope that they-- that we-- we can escape what-- what we didn't escape, anyway.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because at that time, we knew already that they were setting up in a place called Budakalasz, which is another suburb of-- of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the-- in the brick factories, they were setting up a so-called internation camp, where they interned all people.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
